column6: "THE OTHER CONCLUSION"  The next stage in Spidey's history starts here, True Believer!  Changes take many forms.  Peter Parker's stared into the abyss -- but did stare back into him?  Or is he better armed for the next chapter of his life...a chapter that will transform his world even further...and, indeed, the entire Marvel Universe?
column8: | penciller (cover):Mike Deodato | writer:Stan Lee | colorist:Matt Milla | letterer:Cory Petit | inker:Jose Pimentel
